commit_list.message: Read whole data file in query by default
Use alloca instead of fixed buffer in get_admin_names
Fix bug in handling of token names
Trim newlines off the end of lines in tab-separated files
Print more debug information in query mode
Use vector growth factor of 1.5, as it seems to deliver better results
Use tmpfile() to work with the temporary file
Admin names and token parsing changes
Add newlines at the end of each file
Factor out the query loop into a separate function
New serialization scheme for keys of tokens hash map
Fixed bug with incorrect fields in admin codes table
Move the merge algorithm into a separate module
Don't try to lower and trim multi-byte characters
Save some space by compressing vectors that contain only one element
Small fix in the ssh_agent script
Removed some files checked-in by mistake
Use terminal's scrolling ability when under screen
Reload history on each prompt in bash
hinstall alias for quick compilation of haskell packages
Enable color when diffing in git
Don't run ssh-agent in .xinitrc, but start xscreensaver
Fix caps lock remapping and swap mouse buttons
Add a command line argument for ls to handle unicode filenames in cygwin
Move shell configuration files to ~/.rc/ and split them into several independent scripts
Add keybindings to run firefox from xmonad
Set utf-8 as a default coding for screen
Print the exit code of the last command in the command line prompt
.xinitrc: don't run a terminal by default
.vimrc: fix shortcut for running the program with the current file's name
Set less' charset and remove the LESSCHARDEF variable
Don't use nmake as default makeprg in .vimrc
Drop executable flag where not needed
sel update: added screen resize handling
